{"tid":865601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國製造戰機墜毀釀 3 死　緬甸不滿頻出事　改向俄買軍備","createTime":"2018-10-17T07:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T11:13:58.000Z","uid":141151,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"643b35cf9dbfb71e83f89846b549e4a2e8f4b60d","tid":865601,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:46:43.000Z","msg":"中國製造戰機墜毀釀 3 死　緬甸不滿頻出事　改向俄買軍備<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E5%A2%9C%E6%AF%80%E9%87%80-3-%E6%AD%BB-%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E9%A0%BB%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%8B-%E6%94%B9%E5%90%91%E4%BF%84%E8%B2%B7%E8%BB%8D%E5%82%99/?fbclid=IwAR1HYmSNqKNlqjITLvHy9l0wsiozyRQBqZ5X-SLYzPysOyVy5Ap32Vh_5bA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A2%259C%25E6%25AF%2580%25E9%2587%2580-3-%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25BF%2584%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%2582%2599%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1HYmSNqKNlqjITLvHy9l0wsiozyRQBqZ5X-SLYzPysOyVy5Ap32Vh_5bA&d=Z1qCflbjvdOU9%2BWWpJONNgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9a3819bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A2%259C%25E6%25AF%2580%25E9%2587%2580-3-%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25BF%2584%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%2582%2599%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1HYmSNqKNlqjITLvHy9l0wsiozyRQBqZ5X-SLYzPysOyVy5Ap32Vh_5bA&h=4f589471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E5%A2%9C%E6%AF%80%E9%87%80-3-%E6%AD%BB-%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E9%A0%BB%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%8B-%E6%94%B9%E5%90%91%E4%BF%84%E8%B2%B7%E8%BB%8D%E5%82%99/?fbclid=IwAR1HYmSNqKNlqjITLvHy9l0wsiozyRQBqZ5X-SLYzPysOyVy5Ap32Vh_5bA</a><br />\n<br />\n中國製造戰機頻出事，兩架緬甸空軍的殲-7戰機昨在緬甸墜毀，事件造成3人死亡，包括一名11歲女童。《紐約時報》報道，中國製造戰機接連出事，引起緬甸軍方對於中國戰機感到擔憂，已分散進口，改與俄羅斯購買軍備。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍方表示，四架殲-7戰機16日清晨起飛，不料兩架戰機因大霧相繼發生意外，一架墜落稻田，另一架在佛塔附近墜毀。除了2名飛行員罹難，當地1名11歲女童也不幸被飛機的碎片擊中，送醫不治死亡。至於另兩架戰機則安全返回。<br />\n<br />\n中國製的殲-7戰機近日連續在緬甸發生意外，今年4月才發生殲-7戰機「技術故障」，在緬甸中部東籲縣的稻田中墜毀，機上飛行員死亡；去年緬甸軍方1架中國製的運-8運輸機也曾墜落大海，機上122名軍人、機組人員死亡。<br />\n<br />\n連續的墜毀事件再次引起緬甸軍方對中國製造飛機的擔憂，緬甸仰光的泰嘎政治研究所執行董事殷苗亨（U Ye Myo Hein）表示，緬甸的中國飛機，很多已經過時，需要大修。他指出，緬甸軍方對中國不滿，因此已意分散進口，改和俄羅斯購買武器和飛機。<br />\n<br />\n今年8月，緬甸武裝部隊總司令敏昂良，出席在俄羅斯莫斯科的一場軍事博覽會，並簽訂合同，從俄羅斯購買新型武器和飛機。"},{"pid":"5b652bcce8d57e9f302ca0420e2c17f7978f753b","tid":865601,"uid":22481,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"香港地鐵換曬大陸車都出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國製可以摧毀其他國家"},{"pid":"eb8252eb332719f383f6579e380068206a1ad0ae","tid":865601,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"買炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b875cd6b3b425f9f7de68600c48fb0109ed7a12a","tid":865601,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"緬甸人咁憎強國人 仲向強國買軍備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b6c636923fddacde211aaa9f25a12c26193087","tid":865601,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b875cd6b3b425f9f7de68600c48fb0109ed7a12a","tid":865601,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"緬甸人咁憎強國人 仲向強國買軍備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi